title: Gabe Kaplan-Holes And Mellow Rolls-1974 original
description:
MP3
Holes and Mello-Rolls, which included long routines about his high-school days, 
among other topics; the sitcom Welcome Back, Kotter, whose central characters he 
helped Eric Cohen and Alan Sacks create and whose core format he helped them to develop, 
was in part based on his comedy act. In the sitcom, Kaplan played Gabe Kotter,
who returns as a teacher to the dysfunctional high school where he had been a student.
The series ran from 1975-79
